headline: SLB OneSubsea awarded subsea boosting contract by Petrobras for the Búzios field, offshore Brazil
summary: HOUSTON, December 12, 2024--Global energy technology company SLB (NYSE: SLB) today announced a contract award by Petrobras, following a competitive tender, to its OneSubsea™ joint venture for two subsea raw seawater injection (RWI) systems to increase recovery from the prolific Búzios field.
